<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q1_v8" title="Q1_v8" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>
      En un juego de mesa, Ana comienza con 
      <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math>
      puntos. Luego recibe una penalización igual al producto de 
      <m:math><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:math>
      por 
      <m:math><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:math>.
      Esa penalización se resta de su puntaje inicial.
      
      
      ¿Cuál de los siguientes puntajes finales es consistente con esta situación?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math><m:mn>42</m:mn></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Primero, <m:math><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math>. Luego, la penalización es <m:math><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn></m:math>. Como esa penalización se resta del puntaje inicial, el puntaje final es <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mn>42</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Se calcula <m:math><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math>, luego la penalización es <m:math><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn></m:math>, y esa penalización se resta del puntaje inicial: <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Primero, <m:math><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math>. Luego, la penalización es <m:math><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn></m:math>. Como esa penalización se resta del puntaje inicial, resulta <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math>. Por lo tanto, <m:math><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:math> no es consistente con la situación.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>112</m:mn></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Se obtiene <m:math><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math> y la penalización vale <m:math><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn></m:math>. Entonces el puntaje final es <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>112</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Resolver la expresión del paréntesis</strong></p>
            <p>Dentro del producto aparece:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Calcular la penalización</strong></p>
            <p>La penalización es el producto de <m:math><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:math> por <m:math><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, la penalización es de <m:math><m:mn>32</m:mn></m:math> puntos.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Restar la penalización del puntaje inicial</strong></p>
            <p>Ana comienza con <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math> puntos y esa penalización se resta de su puntaje inicial:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El puntaje final consistente con la situación es <m:math><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es la <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>